products.name: Organic English Breakfast Tea
products.description:
English Breakfast Tea is made from both tea plants, camellia sinensis var. sinensis and camellia sinensis var. assamica.

It’s stronger in flavor and contains more caffeine than other teas, but less caffeine than coffee.

English Breakfast Tea offers a variety of health benefits because it contains antioxidants and compounds that can help reduce inflammation in the body.

English breakfast tea will provide enough energy in the morning and a well balanced full bodied flavor. It should be strong enough to handle both milk and sugar, without losing its character.

Health Benefits:

products.name: Organic Raspberry Leaf Tea
products.description:
Raspberry leaf tea is a popular herbal remedy for women. It's been used for centuries to improve women's health and decrease problems with menstruation and pregnancy.

Raspberry Leaf Tea contains vitamins and minerals that are beneficial to our overall health, immune system, and cellular processes. Red raspberry leaves contain vitamin A, vitamin C, vitamin E, and B vitamins. This helps support our health by preventing oxidative stress and improving cellular processes such as maintaining energy levels. The leaves contain calcium, magnesium, and potassium. These minerals help to promote healthy digestion and strong bones.

Raspberry leaf tea contains antioxidants known as polyphenols and tannins. These antioxidants help protect against free radicals that can cause oxidative stress. Oxidative stress can cause a host of issues from increased risk of serious disease to premature aging .

products.name: ADAMS ELDERBERRYS CUTINGS
products.description:
1 Bundle of 5 Cuttings

Adam’s Elderberry plants have a beautiful green foliage and develop large white flower-heads in late spring. These white flowers will develop into beautiful large fruit clusters in the summer. Adam’s Elderberry contains a high amount of vitamin C and has better, consistent quality than wild elderberries. Cold-hardy. Ripens in August.

Shade/Partial Sun/Full Sun

Soil Moisture: Well Drained Soil pH Level 5.5 - 6.5

Taste: Sweet Texture Firm, Juicy

Years to Bear 2 - 3 : Zone Range 3 - 9

SELF POLLINATING

The USDA hardiness zones offer a guide to varieties that will grow well in certain climates. Each zone corresponds to the minimum winter temperatures experienced in a given area. Make sure that your hardiness zone lies within the zone compatibility range of this variety before ordering.

Mature Size

When your plant matures, it will be approximately 6 - 10' tall x 6 - 8' wide.

Recommended Spacing

We recommend spacing these plants 6 - 8' apart to ensure room for growth.

products.name: Mexico Turquesa Chiapas Medium Roast
products.description:
All of our coffee is roasted in The Great State Of Texas!

This Single Origin True Mexican Coffee offers you a sophisticated and clean cup with bright citrus sweetness, delicate chocolate overtones, and complex nutty notes. An Arabica coffee which is "High Grown" in the rich volcanic soil of the Sierre de Madre Chiapas region known as Turquesa, or Turquoise (for the brilliant blue skies), in southern Mexico. These single origin beans are processed by the wet-processed or “washed” method. This means that the fruit skin and pulp were removed from the beans immediately after harvesting and before drying. Additionally, they are put through another level of quality assurance called the "European Prep" method which makes for a much more uniform coffee with no defects. If you enjoy a brew with cocoa/chocolate overtones, this is a great single origin.

products.name: Phoenix Tears Goji Berry
products.description:
1 Bundle of 5 Cuttings

The Phoenix Tears Goji Berry is a highly nutritious, packed plant. Complete with protein and antioxidants, as well as having higher carotene levels than a carrot.

Light purple, bell-shaped flowers bloom in May and continue throughout the summer months. Phoenix Tears Goji berries have a sweet flavor with a mild acidity. The fruit is often dried, canned, or used in smoothies.

At maturity it reaches 5 to 6 feet tall and 5 feet wide.

Goji Berry plants make a beautiful addition to any backyard homestead, orchard, or edible landscape!

The Phoenix Tears Goji is a self-fertile plant!

Cold and drought tolerant

Neutral or somewhat alkaline soil

Zones:3-8

We recommend spacing these plants 5 - 6' apart to ensure room for growth.
